definitions.definition: Late , tardy , overdue , behind (in accomplishing a task, etc.).
Not at the expected point of completion.
labels: of a task or the object of a task
definitions.label_groups: archaic , of a task or the object of a task

definitions.definition: Behind (someone or something moving, a trend, etc.), lagging behind, not keeping up .
Behind in paying a debt ; in arrears .
Not having enough of, lacking ( in something).
Inferior , less advanced (compared with someone in something).
